text: Fencer may refer to: * Fencer, a person who participates in the sport of fencing * Fencer, a person who makes fences * Fencer, the device which energizes an electric fence * Fencer, the NATO reporting name of the Sukhoi Su-24 combat jet * HMS Fencer (D64) * The Fencer (), a 2015 Estonian-Finnish- German film directed by Klaus Härö ==See also== * Fence (disambiguation)
title: Fencer
